This paper deals with the analysis of natural language text, which is a common theme in the sub-category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of formal methods and model representation also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The focus on normative documents and privacy policies suggests a connection to computer security (cs.CR), while the development of a web-based tool suggests a connection to software engineering (cs.SE).
